<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>CreatorPort</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --sweep-wall: #F3F1ED;
      --sweep-floor: #E1DCD4;
      --horizon: #ECE8E1;
      --ink: #181310;
      --ink-soft: #7A736A;
      --ink-faint: #B7AFA4;
      --line: #D6D0C6;
      --page-bg: #FBFAF8;
    }

    html {
      overscroll-behavior: contain;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--page-bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* Default: 200dvh = 100dvh card + 100dvh scroll before peel */
    .card-wrap {
      height: 200dvh;
    }

    /* First card: shorter hold so scroll feels responsive */
    .card-wrap:first-child {
      height: 150dvh;
    }

    /* Last card: no peel needed, just fills viewport */
    .card-wrap:last-child {
      height: 100dvh;
    }

    /* Overlap = 100dvh so next card hides exactly behind current */
    .card-wrap + .card-wrap {
      margin-top: -100dvh;
    }

    .card {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      height: 100dvh;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0 clamp(24px, 6vw, 80px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    /* Descending z-index: Card 1 on top, peels away to reveal Card 2, etc. */
    .card-wrap:nth-child(1) .card { z-index: 6; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(2) .card { z-index: 5; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(3) .card { z-index: 4; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(4) .card { z-index: 3; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(5) .card { z-index: 2; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(6) .card { z-index: 1; }

    .card-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 7vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .card-text {
      font-size: clamp(15px, 2.5vw, 18px);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      max-width: 520px;
    }

    .card-number {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(120px, 20vw, 200px);
      font-weight: 700;
      position: absolute;
      right: clamp(16px, 4vw, 60px);
      bottom: clamp(16px, 4vw, 40px);
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--line);
      opacity: 0.3;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .card-divider {
      width: 48px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--line);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>

    <div class="card-wrap">
      <section class="card" style="background: var(--sweep-wall);">
        <span class="card-label">Welcome</span>
        <h1 class="card-title">CreatorPort HK</h1>
        <div class="card-divider"></div>
        <p class="card-text">Where creators, educators, and makers find their next workshop space in Hong Kong.</p>
        <span class="card-number">1</span>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="card-wrap">
      <section class="card" style="background: var(--page-bg);">
        <span class="card-label">What We Do</span>
        <h2 class="card-title">Workshops that inspire</h2>
        <div class="card-divider"></div>
        <p class="card-text">AI &amp; Robotics, Art, Music, Languages — we connect instructors with curious minds aged 5 to 12 in curated venues across the city.</p>
        <span class="card-number">2</span>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="card-wrap">
      <section class="card" style="background: var(--horizon);">
        <span class="card-label">Summer 2026</span>
        <h2 class="card-title">STEM Summer Camp</h2>
        <div class="card-divider"></div>
        <p class="card-text">Five days of building robots, coding games, and exploring circuits. Small groups, real projects, one unforgettable week.</p>
        <span class="card-number">3</span>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="card-wrap">
      <section class="card" style="background: var(--sweep-wall);">
        <span class="card-label">For Instructors</span>
        <h2 class="card-title">Teach what you love</h2>
        <div class="card-divider"></div>
        <p class="card-text">We handle venues, marketing, and bookings. You bring the expertise. Fair revenue share, zero upfront cost.</p>
        <span class="card-number">4</span>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="card-wrap">
      <section class="card" style="background: var(--page-bg);">
        <span class="card-label">Venues</span>
        <h2 class="card-title">Spaces that work</h2>
        <div class="card-divider"></div>
        <p class="card-text">From coworking studios in Sheung Wan to maker labs in Kwun Tong — flexible rooms booked by the hour or the day.</p>
        <span class="card-number">5</span>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="card-wrap">
      <section class="card" style="background: var(--sweep-floor);">
        <span class="card-label">Get Started</span>
        <h2 class="card-title">Let's build together</h2>
        <div class="card-divider"></div>
        <p class="card-text">Whether you want to teach, learn, or host — we'd love to hear from you. Launching Summer 2026 in Hong Kong.</p>
        <span class="card-number">6</span>
      </section>
    </div>

  </main>
</body>
</html>
